## 2. Vue 2 遗留示例 — 页面入口 batch-off-shelf/index.vue

**要点**：页面目录 kebab-case、接口就近 `./services`、子组件从 `./components` 导入。

```vue
<template>
  <div>
    <el-form inline :model="form" class="filter" size="small" label-width="100px">
      <form-item label="名称：">
        <el-input v-model="form.name" v-trim placeholder="请输入" />
      </form-item>
      <form-item class="filter-actions">
        <el-button type="primary" class="button-small" @click="handleSearch">筛选</el-button>
        <el-button type="text" class="button-reset" @click="handleClear">重置筛选条件</el-button>
      </form-item>
    </el-form>
    <HiTable ref="tableRef" url="Product/batchList" :params="form" @load="handleLoad">
      <template slot="toolbar">
        <el-button size="small" type="primary">批量操作</el-button>
      </template>
      <el-table-column type="selection" width="48" />
      <el-table-column label="名称" prop="name" min-width="100" />
      <el-table-column label="操作" width="120" fixed="right">
        <template slot-scope="scope">
          <el-button type="text" @click="handleEdit(scope.row)">编辑</el-button>
        </template>
      </el-table-column>
    </HiTable>
    <MoveProduct :visible.sync="moveVisible" @success="handleSearch" />
  </div>
</template>

<script>
import HiTable from '@/components/HiTable/index.vue'
import { MoveProduct } from './components'

export default {
  components: { HiTable, MoveProduct },
  data() {
    return {
      form: { name: '' },
      moveVisible: false
    }
  },
  methods: {
    handleSearch() {
      this.$refs.tableRef.reload()
    },
    handleClear() {
      this.form = { name: '' }
      this.handleSearch()
    }
  }
}
</script>

<style lang="scss" scoped>
@import '~styles/tablePage.scss';
</style>
```

