## 7. 公共组件 — components/InputNumber/index.vue

**要点**：跨模块复用放 `components/`，props 精简命名，交互方法以 `handle` 开头。

```vue
<script>
import LibrarySelector from '@/components/LibrarySelector'

export default {
  components: { LibrarySelector },
  props: {
    value: { type: Number, default: 0 },
    min: { type: Number, default: 0 },
    max: { type: Number, default: 999999 }
  },
  methods: {
    handleChange(val) {
      this.$emit('input', val)
    }
  }
}
</script>
```

